data.name: labelNotes.Text
data.value: During the installation process you will be asked to choose a configuration type. A database configuration is recommended for typical deployments of the openECA; the openECA Manager application requires a database to function. The web service and XML configurations available to the openECA are typically used in combination with a master database configuration that is maintained using the openECA Manager. For basic installations you can choose a SQLite database for your configuration with nothing extra to install. MS SQL Server, MySQL and Oracle databases have versions that may be installed for free.
